column5: So far the forecast looks very positive for opening day on LSC: - No rain all week -Gentle wind out of the east -Mid 20's.  Who's attending?
If I could talk the girlfriends dad into it maybe... Lol
Negatory. But hope to get out there for 2 days the following week. Let me know how you make out even if just by PM and I will repay the favour the next week!
